Nočem težav.

00:30:33.523 --> 00:30:36.035
<i>Nobenih težav ni.</i>

00:30:36.443 --> 00:30:38.655
<i>Ali si sam?</i>

00:30:39.345 --> 00:30:41.440
<i>To pa ni varno.</i>

00:30:41.616 --> 00:30:43.866
<i>Nikdar ne smemo ostati sami.</i>

00:30:44.785 --> 00:30:48.558
Čakam prijatelja.
Kmalu bo prišel.

00:30:49.460 --> 00:30:52.489
<i>Lahko ti delam družbo,
dokler ne prispe.</i>

00:30:53.876 --> 00:30:55.884
<i>Se strinjaš?</i>

00:30:58.795 --> 00:31:00.895
Varovala te bom.

00:31:01.903 --> 00:31:05.213
Samo jaz in ti, otročiček.

00:31:07.973 --> 00:31:10.102
Kdo si?

00:31:12.215 --> 00:31:14.887
Kaa.

00:31:20.316 --> 00:31:23.023
Ubogi mladiček.

00:31:23.733 --> 00:31:26.819
Kaj počneš tako globoko v džungli?

00:31:28.155 --> 00:31:30.536
To je moj dom.

00:31:30.594 --> 00:31:33.098
