00:36:13.547 --> 00:36:16.204
Pomagal mi boš,
ker mi dolguješ.

00:36:16.313 --> 00:36:17.117
Kapiraš?

00:36:26.677 --> 00:36:30.146
Tole je najina naloga.
Vidiš to zlato tekočino na steni?

00:36:30.447 --> 00:36:35.588
