00:36:35.679 --> 00:36:41.987
in splezal na vrh
ter mi vrgel tisto brnečo reč.

00:36:44.715 --> 00:36:46.820
Saj nisi resen?

00:36:47.563 --> 00:36:48.889
V bistvu sem.

00:36:49.567 --> 00:36:53.996
Lahko se ubijem!
-Poba, poba ...

00:36:54.159 --> 00:36:57.327
Poskusi razumeti.
Jaz sem medved.

00:36:57.342 --> 00:37:00.413
To pomeni, da moram
vsak dan za zimsko spanje

00:37:00.414 --> 00:37:03.101
